rs for their great support of Caravelle Saigon.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Book now and redeem points! Please contact our Caravelle Rewards team via (84) 2838 234 999 Ext: 27515 or email: caravelle.rewards@caravellehotel.com for further information.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47oihe5t fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7cb28096abfa8b0c0fe5aefa885b506f_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7cb28096abfa8b0c0fe5aefa885b506f_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7cb28096abfa8b0c0fe5aefa885b506f_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7cb28096abfa8b0c0fe5aefa885b506f_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1.jpg\" alt=\"Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-6gsvg21j fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">EARNING POINTS<\/h3>\n<p><\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-47oilskm fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>VND 3,000,000++ = 01 POINT<\/strong> <br \/>Apply for qualified bookings<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">--------------<br \/><strong>MEMBER BENEFITS<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Membership is only for invited clients. <br \/>Upon register to the program, guest will have privilege benefits of:<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6ue1um9j fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">15% off on Best available rate<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">15% off on Spa, Laundry and F&amp;B service<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">10% off for personal banquet event of member<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">01 birthday cake 22cm on memeber' s birthday<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">05 points for every new register member with earning transaction<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><\/div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-6gsvbn88 fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/c750794f3c42d524b1a11d382b1a0525_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-2-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/c750794f3c42d524b1a11d382b1a0525_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-2-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/c750794f3c42d524b1a11d382b1a0525_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-2-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/c750794f3c42d524b1a11d382b1a0525_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-2-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-2.jpg\" alt=\"Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-2\"><div class=\"ffb-id-5galjllt buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Rewards-2023-Eflyer.pdf\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">VIEW DETAILS<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-47oifhmq{ padding-top: 20px;}.ffb-id-5galjllt .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ color:#ffffff;}.ffb-id-5galjllt .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{ color: