n necessary to reflect changing market condition and to tenn.inate the CR programme at any time.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>REDEEMING POINTS:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Members may check their CR Point balance and redeem their CR Points for Rewards by<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Written redemption request sent directly to caravelle.rewards@caravellehotel.com<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; CR reward points should be claimed within O 1 year from the Member's checks out date, expired points will be automatically eliminated from the total balance without notice<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Upon redemption, members shall collect their Reward Ceriificates for Caravelle Saigon products and services. Members shall state their intention to use the Reward Certificates at the point of reservation. Utilisation of the Reward Certificates is subject to availability<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>REWARD CERTIFICATES:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Rewards are subject to availability at time of request. The address to deliver the rewards should be notified. Caravelle Saigon Product and Services: Reward certificates are valid for 06 months from the date of issue and are non-transferable, unless stated otherwise. Reward Certificates of Caravelle Saigon Productions and services are available to collect after 05 working days. Members shall state their intention to use the Reward Certificates at the point of reservation. Utilisation of the Reward Certificates is subject to availability. Unused Reward Certificates may not be extended, returned for credit to the Member&rsquo;s accounts, or exchanged for cash.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>MEMBER&rsquo;S RESPONSIBILITY:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">It is the Members&rsquo; responsibility to quote their CR membership number when making reservations. Members who are missing credit from their CR member account should notify the CR Membership Services within 60 days from the check-out date. Otherwise, the relevant CR Points will be forfeited. Any claims for missing CR Points can be forwarded to CR Membership Services via email. Whenever there is a change of personal profile, it is the Member&rsquo;s sole responsibility to inform CR Membership Services in writing. Points cannot be redeemed after resignation.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-47oifhmq{ \npadding-top: 20px;\n\n}\n.ffb-id-5galjllt .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ \ncolor:#ffffff;\n}\n.ffb-id-5galjllt .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{ \ncolor:#ffffff;\n}\n.ffb-id-5galjllt .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ \nborder-color: transparent;\n}\n.ffb-id-5galjllt .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{ \nborder-color: transparent;\n}\n.ffb-id-5galjllt .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ \nbackground-color:#490042;\n}\n.ffb-id-5galjllt .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{ \nbackground-color:#490042;\n}\n.ffb-id-5galjllt{ \npadding-top: 10px;\npadding-bottom: 20px;\n\n}\n@media (min-width:768px) { \n.ffb-id-5galjllt{ \npadding-top: 10px;\npadding-bottom: 20px;\n\n}\n}@media (min-width:992px) { \n.ffb-id-5galjllt{ \npadding-top: 10px;\npadding-bottom: 20px;\n\n}\n}@media (min-width:1200px) { \n.ffb-id-5galjllt{ \npadding-top: 10px;\npadding-bottom: 20px;\n\n}\n}.ffb-id-6gsvg21j ,\n.ffb-id-6gsvg21j:before,\n.ffb-id-6gsvg21j:after,\n.ffb-id-6gsvg21j *,\n.ffb-id-6gsvg21j *:before,\n.ffb-id-6gsvg21j *:after{ \ncolor: #490042 !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-6gsvg21j{ \nfont-family: Georgia, serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-6gsvg21j:before,\n.ffb-id-6gsvg21j:after,\n.ffb-id-6gsvg21j:hover,\n